list.name: Default
list.comment: Added a controller in DatabaseUtils for the new property, 'backend', in the hibernate config file. The controller reads the hibernate file and checks for what the backend property is set to. This was added to dynamically update db connection settings at runtime if needed. Simplified programming into smaller, more reusable methods.

task.summary: WebUtils table building methods made more generalized. Added a controller method to handle generalizations and simplify adding new dynamic content methods later on.
Cleaned up WebUtils a bit more.
Fixed bug where quickquote was returning a blank page with no error message for user when the user searched for an invalid stock symbol.
Brought code coverage up to 100% coverage.

Hibernate update config correctly updates with DOCTYPE. Added a new property to hibernate config called 'backend'. This will be used to run updates to config file based on backend setting.
